<div class="page" title="Page 2"><div class="section"><div class="layoutArea"><div class="column"><p>Committees are a huge part of life at Butler, responsible for organising our charity fundraisers, campaigning for environmental causes, volunteering all around Durham, designing posters for our events, and much, much more. They&rsquo;re a great way to get involved, learn new skills, meet loads of lovely people and give back to the community!</p><p>If you want to get involved or have any ideas, please come along to the committee meetings or get in touch!&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div>